                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>Not that auto gain is the solution, but a gain control on output would be helpful. Bypass is still low :( How do I fix this?</p>
<p>UPDATE: I fixed it myself using "Audio MIDI Setup.app" on my Mac. For some reason the first 2 channels were lowered. Raised them and now problem solved! Nice and loud again!</p>
