                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>I realize this post is old-ish.. but it seems like whatever your output of your computer is BEFORE you turn on the app, directly correlates to the output of the app itself.  ie... turn your computer all the way up before turning on the app. then you have full headroom when Sonarworks is running. - note: I am using the headphone edition.</p></section>
              </div>

