                    </span>
                  </div>

                  

                  
                </div>

                <section class="comment-body font-light"><p>Hi Stéphane, </p>
<p>We have fixed the the volume jumps with the latest 4.2.2.21 software release too. Find the download <a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/reference/downloads" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">here</a> and simply install the update (it will replace the older version).</p>
<p>Once complete, head to Systemwide settings and make sure that Adjust The Output Device Gain setting is checked - you should no longer get the volume jumps regardless of what the system volume is set to. Thank you!</p>
<p><img src="/hc/user_images/Kf61xlX07alPB3FGe-vbPA.png"></p></section>
              </div>

